description: How do you turn a straight guy into doing something gay I ask. Well, how about catch him on video jerking off in the shower, and tell him that if he does more, he could make lots of money. That is exactly what this two roommates did. At first I thought that the guy will get so mad, but it turned out he didnt mind is so much. After calling a few other friends to come over, and drinking some shots, everyone was willing to make that extra dough. This dorm party turned into a big gay fuck fest real quick.
title: All In
